            Such moral outrage is common
among the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">opponents</ENAMEX> of globalization--of the transfer of technology and capital
from high-wage to low-wage <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE_DESC">countries</ENAMEX> and the resulting growth of
