anyone with a good word for this process is naive or corrupt and, in either
case, a de facto <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">agent</ENAMEX> of global capital in its oppression of <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">workers</ENAMEX> here and
